Class MusicCD

java.lang.Object
LibraryItem
MusicCD
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<LibraryItem>
public class MusicCD extends LibraryItem
MusicCD is a concrete subclass of LibraryItem that represents a music CD in the library. It extends LibraryItem with music-specific properties such as artist, composer, and label.
